<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609918859" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span>——一个在思考生物如何在当今社会生存下去的小写手</p>
<p><strong>特别鸣谢：</strong><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662223&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609918859" alt="pokm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662223)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;">pokm</a></span><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609918859" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609918859" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>作者的话：</strong></p>
<p>如果实在看不懂的话，可以先行移步前往讨论区，pokm佬的解读十分正确。<br />
2018年6月25日并非是无意，可以去查一下这天到底发生了什么与导弹、国际机场、首都有关的新闻。</p>
<p>同时这个点子是我在听一首曲子的时候想出来的，在这里推一下：</p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=515414031&auto=0&height=66"></iframe><br />
里面有一段评论：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>一个叙利亚父亲抱住慌张的孩子说到：不怕那只是颗流星</p>
</blockquote>
<p>愿世上再无战争。</p>
